data.description: This is an amazing opportunity to become the owner of a beautiful single-level home located in Westbrook Village, an adult Community. Shopping, freeways, sporting events, and medical facilities are all within a short drive from your new home. Just minutes away from the Westbrook Village Golf Club, this property offers a host of amenities such as two recreation centers, pickleball and tennis courts, swimming pools, spas, and much more. With a newly installed leased solar system, you can enjoy potential savings on electricity costs for years to come. As you step inside, you'll notice the pride of ownership and impeccable attention to detail. The interior boasts a welcoming living room, a family room, and a spacious kitchen with plenty of cabinets, ideal for friendly gatherings and family holiday celebrations. The screened-in patio is perfect for relaxing afternoons while the spacious backyard has fruit trees, a luscious green turf, and a mister system, making it an exquisite outdoor space. This property is a must-see, so don't delay making it your new home!
